2026-03-18 12:08:42,996 | INFO | {'prd_text': 'Product Requirement Document (PRD)\n\nProject Name: ShopSphere\nProduct Type: Amazon-like E-commerce Web Platform\n\n1. Product Overview\nGoal\n\nBuild a scalable e-commerce platform similar to Amazon where users can browse products, add items to a cart, purchase products, and track orders.\n\nObjectives\n\nProvide a smooth shopping experience\n\nEnable sellers to list and manage products\n\nAllow admins to manage the marketplace\n\nSupport millions of users\n\nPlatform\n\nPrimary platform:\n\nWeb application (desktop + mobile responsive)\n\n2. Target Users\nCustomer\n\nCustomers should be able to:\n\nBrowse products\n\nSearch products\n\nAdd items to cart\n\nPlace orders\n\nTrack orders\n\nLeave reviews\n\nSeller\n\nSellers should be able to:\n\nAdd products\n\nUpdate product information\n\nManage inventory\n\nView sales analytics\n\nTrack orders\n\nAdmin\n\nAdmins should be able to:\n\nManage users\n\nRemove products\n\nMonitor platform activity\n\nManage orders\n\nView platform analytics\n\n3. Core Features\n3.1 Authentication System\n\nUsers should be able to:\n\nSign up\n\nLog in\n\nLog out\n\nReset password\n\nRoles\n\nCustomer\nSeller\nAdmin\n\nSecurity\n\nJWT authentication\n\nPassword hashing\n\nEmail verification\n\n3.2 Product Catalog\n\nUsers should be able to:\n\nBrowse categories\n\nSearch products\n\nFilter products\n\nView product details\n\nProduct Fields\n\ntitle\ndescription\nprice\nrating\nimages\nseller_id\ncategory_id\nstock_quantity\n\n3.3 Product Categories\n\nExample categories:\n\nElectronics\nClothing\nBooks\nHome Appliances\nBeauty\nToys\n\nUsers can filter products by:\n\ncategory\n\nprice\n\nrating\n\npopularity\n\n3.4 Product Detail Page\n\nEach product page should display:\n\nproduct images\n\ntitle\n\nprice\n\ndescription\n\nrating\n\nreviews\n\nseller information\n\nActions available:\n\nAdd to cart\nBuy now\n\n3.5 Shopping Cart\n\nUsers can:\n\nAdd product to cart\n\nRemove product\n\nUpdate quantity\n\nView total price\n\nCart must persist per user account.\n\n3.6 Checkout System\n\nUser checkout flow:\n\nCart → Address → Payment → Order Confirmation\n\nUsers must be able to:\n\nadd shipping address\n\nchoose payment method\n\nconfirm purchase\n\n3.7 Order Management\n\nEach order includes:\n\norder_id\nuser_id\nproducts\ntotal_price\npayment_status\nshipping_status\ncreated_at\n\nOrder Status\n\nOrder placed\nProcessing\nShipped\nOut for delivery\nDelivered\n\n3.8 Order History\n\nUsers can view:\n\nprevious orders\n\norder details\n\norder status\n\n3.9 Seller Dashboard\n\nSellers should be able to:\n\nadd product\n\nedit product\n\ndelete product\n\nmanage stock\n\nview orders\n\nview sales analytics\n\nAnalytics examples:\n\ntotal sales\ntotal orders\ntop selling products\n\n3.10 Admin Panel\n\nAdmins should be able to:\n\nremove inappropriate products\n\nmanage sellers\n\nmanage users\n\nmonitor orders\n\nview platform analytics\n\n4. Non-Functional Requirements\nPerformance\n\nPage load time < 2 seconds.\n\nScalability\n\nSystem must support 1 million users.\n\nSecurity\n\nHTTPS required\nInput validation\nSecure authentication\n\nReliability\n\nSystem uptime target:\n\n99.9%\n\n5. Suggested Tech Stack\nFrontend\n\nReact\nNext.js\nTailwind CSS\n\nBackend\n\nPython\nFastAPI\n\nDatabase\n\nPostgreSQL\n\nSearch\n\nElasticsearch\n\nCaching\n\nRedis\n\nDeployment\n\nDocker\nKubernetes (optional)\n\n6. API Examples\nGet products\n\nGET /products\n\nGet product details\n\nGET /products/{id}\n\nAdd to cart\n\nPOST /cart/add\n\nRemove from cart\n\nDELETE /cart/remove\n\nPlace order\n\nPOST /orders\n\nGet orders\n\nGET /orders\n\n7. Database Entities\n\nMain tables:\n\nusers\nproducts\norders\ncart_items\ncategories\nreviews\n\nExample Schema\nUsers\n\nid\nname\nemail\npassword_hash\nrole\ncreated_at\n\nProducts\n\nid\ntitle\ndescription\nprice\nstock\ncategory_id\nseller_id\ncreated_at\n\nOrders\n\nid\nuser_id\ntotal_price\npayment_status\nshipping_status\ncreated_at\n\n8. Figma Design Specification\n\nThis defines the UI layout that the Figma MCP integration will provide.\n\nHomepage Layout\n\nSections:\n\nNavbar\nSearch Bar\nCategory Sidebar\nFeatured Banner\nProduct Grid\nFooter\n\nLayout Structure\n---------------------------------\n| Logo | Search | Cart | Profile |\n---------------------------------\n| Category Menu                 |\n---------------------------------\n| Featured Banner               |\n---------------------------------\n| Product Grid                  |\n---------------------------------\n| Footer                        |\n---------------------------------\nProduct Card Component\n\nEach product card contains:\n\nProduct image\nProduct title\nPrice\nRating\nAdd to cart button\n\nLayout\n+------------------+\n| Product Image    |\n|                  |\n+------------------+\n| Product Title    |\n| $Price           |\n| ⭐ Rating        |\n| Add to Cart      |\n+------------------+\nProduct Detail Page\n\nSections:\n\nImage gallery\nProduct title\nPrice\nRating\nDescription\nAdd to cart\nBuy now\nReviews\n\nLayout\n---------------------------------\n| Images | Product Title        |\n|        | Price                |\n|        | Rating               |\n|        | Add to Cart          |\n---------------------------------\n| Product Description           |\n---------------------------------\n| Reviews                       |\n---------------------------------\nCart Page\n--------------------------------\n| Product | Qty | Price | Remove|\n--------------------------------\n| Order Summary                |\n| Total Price                  |\n| Checkout Button              |\n--------------------------------\nSeller Dashboard Layout\n\nSections:\n\nProduct list\nAdd product\nEdit product\nSales analytics\nOrder management\n\nDesign System\nColors\n\nUse the same couls as the mastercard colour paterns from graphit componennt.\n\nFonts\n\nPrimary Font: Inter\n\nHeadings: Bold\nBody Text: Regular\n\nFigma Components\n\nThe following components must exist in the Figma file for MCP extraction:\n\nNavbar\nProductCard\nProductGrid\nCategorySidebar\nCartItem\nOrderSummary\nFooter', 'figma_image_path': 'inputs/figma.png', 'system_spec': {'frontend': 'React, Next.js, Tailwind CSS', 'backend': 'Python, FastAPI', 'database': 'PostgreSQL', 'features': ['Authentication System', 'Product Catalog', 'Product Categories', 'Product Detail Page', 'Shopping Cart', 'Checkout System', 'Order Management', 'Order History', 'Seller Dashboard', 'Admin Panel'], 'pages': ['Homepage', 'Product Detail Page', 'Cart Page', 'Seller Dashboard'], 'components': ['Navbar', 'ProductCard', 'ProductGrid', 'CategorySidebar', 'CartItem', 'OrderSummary', 'Footer']}, 'pages': ['Homepage', 'Product Detail Page', 'Cart Page', 'Seller Dashboard'], 'components': ['Navbar', 'ProductCard', 'ProductGrid', 'CategorySidebar', 'CartItem', 'OrderSummary', 'Footer'], 'architecture_plan': {'architecture_type': 'Monolithic', 'backend': {'framework': 'FastAPI', 'modules': ['Authentication System', 'Product Catalog', 'Shopping Cart', 'Checkout System', 'Order Management', 'Seller Dashboard', 'Admin Panel']}, 'database': {'tables': ['users', 'products', 'categories', 'orders', 'order_items', 'cart_items', 'product_categories']}, 'frontend': {'framework': 'Next.js', 'pages': ['Homepage', 'Product Detail Page', 'Cart Page', 'Seller Dashboard']}, 'apis': ['Authentication API', 'Product API', 'Category API', 'Cart API', 'Order API', 'Seller Dashboard API', 'Admin Panel API']}, 'task_plan': {'backend_tasks': ['Implement Authentication System module using FastAPI', 'Develop Product Catalog module using FastAPI', 'Create Shopping Cart module using FastAPI', 'Design Checkout System module using FastAPI', 'Build Order Management module using FastAPI', 'Develop Seller Dashboard module using FastAPI', 'Create Admin Panel module using FastAPI'], 'database_tasks': ['Create users table', 'Create products table', 'Create categorie